
Repository for WHDLoad install sources
--------------------------------------

Builds ready to release install archives from sources.

Supported platforms: Linux, MacOS, Amiga
Requires:
- GNU Make
- vasm or basm
- lha
Requires on Amiga:
- WDate (https://whdload.de/whdload/WHDLoad_dev.lha)
- perl (https://aminet.net/package/dev/gg/perl571)

Make targets:
			build Slave (default)
	img		build RawDIC Slave
	dest		copy Slave/ReadMe to install directory for testing
	inst		build install package
	arc		build install package archive
	rel		copy install archive to release location
	clean		remove all generated artefacts

